1.2.name: wordpress/blinko-broadcaster
1.2.description: The BlinkoTV Broadcaster Plugin gives any WordPress user the opportunity to create their own broadcasting station, by signing up for a BlinkoTV account, all through a user-friendly interface in the Admin Panel.
